      "content": "That feeling of invisibility is a heavy weight to carry, but remember that even in the midst of strangers, your presence matters in the quiet moments you share with your own heart. While it may feel like nothing changes without you, the absence of your own internal struggle would be a significant shift in your life's narrative. You are not a ghost; you are a person who can choose to make yourself seen, even if only to yourself, by finding a quiet way to be present.",
